{"id":119346,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/简讯：山西矿难责任人被判死刑/","date":"2010-11-03T20:39:44Z","modified":"2010-11-03T20:39:44Z","title":"简讯：山西矿难责任人被判死刑","content":"<div>\n<p>山西7月发生的一起矿难事件的责任人被判处死刑。</p>\n<p>矿主蔡永胜被控非法买卖和储存爆炸物。</p>\n<p>蔡永胜在山西翼城刘沟煤矿非法储存炸药1404公斤、雷管9300枚。</p>\n<p>7月31日凌晨2时40分左右炸药自燃爆炸，造成17人死亡，44人受伤。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/w5Mxi1vXc2gmLh6nf4hU3jB3i3A/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/w5Mxi1vXc2gmLh6nf4hU3jB3i3A/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/w5Mxi1vXc2gmLh6nf4hU3jB3i3A/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/w5Mxi1vXc2gmLh6nf4hU3jB3i3A/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=3H8d0xzw1_c:Ts1o-CZ1R9s:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=3H8d0xzw1_c:Ts1o-CZ1R9s:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=3H8d0xzw1_c:Ts1o-CZ1R9s:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=3H8d0xzw1_c:Ts1o-CZ1R9s:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=3H8d0xzw1_c:Ts1o-CZ1R9s:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=3H8d0xzw1_c:Ts1o-CZ1R9s:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/3H8d0xzw1_c\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/11/